‚ÄúThen l'Il go without. | don‚Äôt care what people say!‚Äù cried 
Jo, taking up her book. 

‚ÄúYou may have it, you may! only don‚Äôt stain it, and do 
behave nicely. Don‚Äôt put your hands behind you, or stare, or 
say ‚ÄòChristopher Columbus!‚Äô will you?‚Äù 

‚ÄúDon‚Äôt worry about me; l'Il be as prim as I can, and not get 
