‚ÄúServes me right for trying to be fine. | wish I‚Äôd let my hair 
alone,‚Äù cried Meg petulantly. 

‚ÄúSo do l, it was so smooth and pretty. But it will soon grow 
out again,‚Äù said Beth, coming to kiss and comfort the shorn 


