But the boy laughed, and said pleasantly, though he 
looked a little startled‚Äî 

‚ÄúDon‚Äôt mind me; stay, if you like.‚Äù 


‚ÄúShan‚Äôt | disturb you?‚Äù 

‚ÄúNot a bit; | only came here because | don‚Äôt know many 
