‚ÄúHush! Don‚Äôt say anything,‚Äù she whispered, adding aloud, 
‚ÄúIt‚Äôs nothing. | turned my foot a little, that‚Äôs all‚Äù; and limped 
upstairs to put her things on. 

Hannah scolded, Meg cried, and Jo was at her wits‚Äô end, till 
