‚ÄúO sir, they do care, very, very much!‚Äù 

‚ÄúAre you the musical girl?‚Äù he asked, without any startling 
‚ÄúHey!‚Äù as he looked down at her very kindly. 

‚ÄúI‚Äôm Beth. | love it dearly, and l'Il come, if you are quite 
sure nobody will hear me‚Äîand be disturbed,‚Äù she added, 
