‚ÄúNot a soul, my dear. The house is empty half the day; so 
come, and drum away as much as you like, and | shall be 
obliged to you.‚Äù 


‚ÄúHow kind you are, sir!‚Äù 

Beth blushed like a rose under the friendly look he wore; 
but she was not frightened now, and gave the big hand a 
