‚Äú| didn‚Äôt say anything about his eyes, and | don‚Äôt see why 
you need fire up when | admire his riding.‚Äù 

‚ÄúOh, my goodness! that little goose means a centaur, and 
she called him a Cyclops,‚Äù exclaimed Jo, with a burst of 
