VIII 


Jo Meets APOLLYON 


‚ÄúGirls, where are you going?‚Äù asked Amy, coming into their 
room one Saturday afternoon, and finding them getting 
ready to go out, with an air of secrecy which excited her 
Curiosity. 

‚ÄúNever mind; little girls shouldn‚Äôt ask questions,‚Äù returned 
Jo sharply. 

Now if there /s anything mortifying to our feelings, when 
