My child, the troubles and temptations of your life are 
beginning, and may be many; but you can overcome and 
outlive them all if you learn to feel the strength and 
tenderness of your Heavenly Father as you do that of your 
earthly one. The more you love and trust Him, the nearer 
you will feel to Him, and the less you will depend on human 
power and wisdom. His love and care never tire or change, 
can never be taken from you, but may become the source of 
lifelong peace, happiness, and strength. Believe this 
