As if she heard, Amy opened her eyes, and held out her 
arms, with a smile that went straight to Jo‚Äôs heart. Neither 
said a word, but they hugged one another close, in spite of 
the blankets, and everything was forgiven and forgotten in 
one hearty kiss. 


IX 


Mec Goes To VANITY Fair 


‚ÄúI do think it was the most fortunate thing in the world that 
those children should have the measles just now,‚Äù said Meg, 
one April day, as she stood packing the ‚Äúgo abroady‚Äù trunk 
