Mr. Brooke looked up, and said quickly, ‚ÄúYoung ladies in 
America love independence as much as their ancestors did, 
and are admired and respected for supporting themselves.‚Äù 

‚ÄúOh, yes; of course it‚Äôs very nice and proper in them to do 
so. We have many most respectable and worthy young 
