‚ÄúDid the German song suit, Miss March?‚Äù inquired 
Mr. Brooke, breaking an awkward pause. 

‚ÄúOh, yes! it was very sweet, and I‚Äôm much obliged to 
whoever translated it for me;‚Äù and Meg‚Äôs downcast face 
