‚ÄúDon‚Äôt you read German?‚Äù asked Miss Kate, with a look of 
surprise. 

‚ÄúNot very well. My father, who taught me, is away, and | 
don‚Äôt get on very fast alone, for I‚Äôve no one to correct my 
