‚Äú| dote upon it; my sister Meg used to ride when papa was 
rich, but we don‚Äôt keep any horses now, except Ellen Tree,‚Äù 
added Amy, laughing. 


‚ÄúTell me about Ellen Tree; is it a donkey?‚Äù asked Grace 
Curiously. 

‚ÄúWhy, you see, Jo is crazy about horses, and so am I, but 
