her shy yet friendly way‚Äî 

‚ÄúI‚Äôm afraid you are tired; can | do anything for you?‚Äù 

‚ÄúTalk to me, please; it‚Äôs dull, sitting by myself,‚Äù answered 
Frank, who had evidently been used to being made much of 
