‚ÄúIf | tell mine, will you tell yours?‚Äù 


‚ÄúYes, if the girls will too.‚Äù 

‚ÄúWe will. Now, Laurie.‚Äù 

‚ÄúAfter I'd seen as much of the world as | want to, I'd like to 
