‚ÄúSaw it.‚Äù 

‚ÄúWhere?‚Äù 

‚ÄúPocket.‚Äù 

‚ÄúAll this time?‚Äù 

‚ÄúYes; isn‚Äôt that romantic?‚Äù 

‚ÄúNo, it‚Äôs horrid.‚Äù 

‚ÄúDon‚Äôt you like it?‚Äù 

‚ÄúOf course | don‚Äôt. It‚Äôs ridiculous; it won‚Äôt be allowed. My 
