‚Äú| want to tell you something, mother.‚Äù 

‚ÄúAbout Meg?‚Äù 

‚ÄúHow quickly you guessed! Yes, it‚Äôs about her, and though 
it‚Äôs a little thing, it fidgets me.‚Äù 

‚ÄúBeth is asleep; speak low, and tell me all about it. That 
