over her sewing, with a timid, troubled look on her face. To 
her mother‚Äôs inquiries she answered that she was quite well, 
and Jo‚Äôs she silenced by begging to be let alone. 

‚ÄúShe feels it in the air‚Äîlove, | mean‚Äîand she‚Äôs going very 
