regretted the past, and she wished she had held her tongue. 

‚ÄúHe won't do it unless he is very much worried, and only 
threatens it sometimes, when he gets tired of studying. | 
often think | should like to, especially since my hair was cut; 
so, if you ever miss us, you may advertise for two boys, and 
