‚ÄúNo; he was pretty mild, on the whole.‚Äù 

‚ÄúAh! | got it all round; even you cast me off over there, and 
| felt just ready to go to the deuce,‚Äù he began apologetically. 

‚ÄúDon‚Äôt talk in that way; turn over a new leaf and begin 
