delicious grapes the ‚ÄúJungfrau‚Äù had sent her. 

‚ÄúSo am |,‚Äù added Jo, slapping the pocket wherein reposed 
the long-desired Undine and Sintram. 

‚ÄúI‚Äôm sure | am,‚Äù echoed Amy, poring over the engraved 
copy of the Madonna and Child, which her mother had given 
