‚ÄúWhere is John?‚Äù asked Meg anxiously. 

‚ÄúStopped to get the license for tomorrow, ma‚Äôam.‚Äù 

‚ÄúWhich side won the last match, Teddy?‚Äù inquired Jo, who 
persisted in feeling an interest in manly sports, despite her 


