‚ÄúDon‚Äôt lecture any more, there‚Äôs a good soul! | have 
enough all through the week, and like to enjoy myself when 
| come home. l'Il get myself up regardless of expense, 
tomorrow, and be a Satisfaction to my friends.‚Äù 

‚ÄúI'll leave you in peace if you'll only let your hair grow. I‚Äôm 
not aristocratic, but | do object to being seen with a person 
