Shiver. 

‚ÄúIt‚Äôs worse than boots, it‚Äôs a silk dress,‚Äù she said, with the 
calmness of desperation, for she wanted the worst over. 

‚ÄúWell, dear, what is the ‚Äòdem‚Äôd total,‚Äô as Mr. Mantalini 
Says?‚Äù 

That didn‚Äôt sound like John, and she knew he was looking 
