‚ÄúTwins, by Jupiter!‚Äù was all he said for a minute; then, 
turning to the women with an appealing look that was 
comically piteous, he added, ‚ÄúTake ‚Äôem quick, somebody! 

I‚Äôm going to laugh, and | shall drop ‚Äôem.‚Äù 


John rescued his babies, and marched up and down, with 
one on each arm, as if already initiated into the mysteries of 
