for her misdemeanors. 

‚ÄúHow shall | behave here?‚Äù she asked, as they approached 
the third mansion. 

‚ÄúJust as you please; | wash my hands of you,‚Äù was Amy‚Äôs 
short answer. 

‚ÄúThen l'Il enjoy myself. The boys are at home, and we'll 
have a comfortable time. Goodness knows | need a little 
change, for elegance has a bad effect upon my 
