‚ÄúIt‚Äôs too bad, for there is no time to make other things, and 
| don‚Äôt want to fill up with odds and ends. The table was just 
complete then: now it‚Äôs spoilt.‚Äù 

‚Äú| dare say she‚Äôd put them back if you asked her,‚Äù 
suggested someone. 

‚ÄúHow could | after all the fuss?‚Äù began May, but she did 
