eighteen, but we don‚Äôt realize it, and treat her like a child, 
forgetting she‚Äôs a woman.‚Äù 

‚ÄúSo she is. Dear heart, how fast you do grow up,‚Äù returned 
her mother, with a sigh and a smile. 


‚ÄúCan't be helped, Marmee, so you must resign yourself to 
