‚ÄúHappy woman! I‚Äôve got heaps.‚Äù 

‚ÄúMy dear, what are they?‚Äù 

‚ÄúI'll settle Bethy‚Äôs troubles, and then l'Il tell you mine. 
They are not very wearing, so they'll keep;‚Äù and Jo stitched 
