XXXIII 


Jo‚Äôs JOURNAL 


‚ÄúNew York, November. 
‚ÄúDeaR MARMEE AND BETH‚Äî 
‚ÄúI‚Äôm going to write you a regular volume, for I‚Äôve 
got heaps to tell, though I‚Äôm not a fine young lady 
travelling on the continent. When | lost sight of 
father‚Äôs dear old face, | felt a trifle blue, and might 
