‚ÄúTuesday Eve. 
‚ÄúHad a lively time in my seminary, this morning, 
for the children acted like Sancho; and at one time 
| really thought | should shake them all round. 
Some good angel inspired me to try gymnastics, 
and | kept it up till they were glad to sit down and 
