man caused Amy to pity the four plain Misses Davis from the 
bottom of her heart. 

‚ÄúHere are your flowers; | arranged them myself, 
remembering that you didn‚Äôt like what Hannah calls a ‚Äòsot- 
bookay,‚Äô‚Äù said Laurie, handing her a delicate nosegay, in a 
