‚ÄúBut it can‚Äôt be right for him to neglect me.‚Äù 

‚ÄúDon‚Äôt you neglect him?‚Äù 

‚ÄúWhy, mother, | thought you‚Äôd take my part!‚Äù 

‚ÄúSo I do, as far as sympathizing goes; but I think the fault 
