showed that it did, by the cordial tone in which she said‚Äî 

‚ÄúI‚Äôm glad of that! | didn‚Äôt think you‚Äôd been a very bad boy, 
but | fancied you might have wasted money at that wicked 
Baden-Baden, lost your heart to some charming 
Frenchwoman with a husband, or got into some of the 
