‚ÄúI‚Äôm all ready for the secrets;‚Äù and he glanced up with a 
decided expression of interest in his eyes. 

‚ÄúI‚Äôve none to tell; you may begin.‚Äù 

‚ÄúHaven't one to bless myself with. | thought perhaps you‚Äôd 
had some news from home.‚Äù 

‚ÄúYou have heard all that has come lately. Don‚Äôt you hear 
often? | fancied Jo would send you volumes.‚Äù 

‚ÄúShe‚Äôs very busy; I‚Äôm roving about so, it‚Äôs impossible to be 
