‚ÄúI wish you‚Äôd do me the favor to rouse yourself a little,‚Äù 
she said sharply. 

‚ÄúDo it for me, there‚Äôs a dear girl.‚Äù 

‚ÄúI could, if | tried;‚Äù and she looked as if she would like 
