idea into your head, lest you should write and congratulate 
them before the thing was settled.‚Äù 

‚ÄúI‚Äôm not the scatterbrain | was; you may trust me, I‚Äôm 
sober and sensible enough for anyone‚Äôs confidante now.‚Äù 

‚ÄúSo you are, dear, and | should have made you mine, only | 
fancied it might pain you to learn that your Teddy loved 
