‚Äú| do;‚Äù and Mrs. March smiled her wise smile, as Jo turned 
back the leaves to read what Amy said of Laurie. 

‚ÄúIt is so beautiful to be loved as Laurie loves me; he isn‚Äôt 
sentimental, doesn‚Äôt say much about it, but | see and feel it 
