any other feminine fib proper to the occasion; instead of 
which that undignified creature answered, with an 
irrepressible sob‚Äî 

‚ÄúBecause you are going away.‚Äù 

‚ÄúAch, mein Gott, that is so good!‚Äù cried Mr. Bhaer, 
managing to clasp his hands in spite of the umbrella and the 
